opportunity for him

00:00:27.550 --> 00:00:29.790 align:middle line:84%
to join us again because
I had so many more

00:00:29.790 --> 00:00:35.400 align:middle line:84%
questions about realizing our
huge, beautiful, full human

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:36.680 align:middle line:90%
potential.

00:00:36.680 --> 00:00:39.690 align:middle line:84%
