00:00:42.070 --> 00:00:44.760 align:middle line:84%
Is this something that
you call Shaktipat.

00:00:44.760 --> 00:00:45.760 align:middle line:90%
>>BASKARAN PILLAI: Yeah.

00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:47.965 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Could you explain
what Shaktipat is?

00:00:47.965 --> 00:00:50.010 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Shakti is energy.

00:00:50.010 --> 00:00:53.660 align:middle line:84%
It's the Sanskrit word
which means the energy.

00:00:53.660 --> 00:00:54.555 align:middle line:90%
Pat is transmission.

00:00:54.555 --> 00:00:58.100 align:middle line:90%


00:00:58.100 --> 00:01:00.170 align:middle line:84%
This is something I
told Wayne Dyer, too.

00:01:00.170 --> 00:01:01.850 align:middle line:90%


00:01:01.850 --> 00:01:05.695 align:middle line:84%
I can give a talk for
two hours, three hours.

00:01:05.695 --> 00:01:06.920 align:middle line:90%


00:01:06.920 --> 00:01:08.520 align:middle line:90%
It's an intellectual exercise.

00:01:08.520 --> 00:01:09.860 align:middle line:90%


00:01:09.860 --> 00:01:12.150 align:middle line:84%
You may or may
not appreciate it.

00:01:12.150 --> 00:01:14.140 align:middle line:90%
And then you leave.

00:01:14.140 --> 00:01:18.320 align:middle line:84%
But Shaktipat is something
where no words are used.

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:19.500 align:middle line:90%


00:01:19.500 --> 00:01:21.059 align:middle line:90%
It is a transmission.

00:01:21.059 --> 00:01:21.850 align:middle line:90%
It is my intention.

00:01:21.850 --> 00:01:22.890 align:middle line:90%


00:01:22.890 --> 00:01:26.086 align:middle line:84%
It is the intention
of the teacher

00:01:26.086 --> 00:01:34.870 align:middle line:84%
to go and enter the
consciousness of the students

00:01:34.870 --> 00:01:37.520 align:middle line:84%
to make changes in
his consciousness.

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:39.590 align:middle line:90%


00:01:39.590 --> 00:01:41.604 align:middle line:90%
So silently, without words.

00:01:41.604 --> 00:01:43.750 align:middle line:90%


00:01:43.750 --> 00:01:47.920 align:middle line:84%
So this is what happened when
I said in the last interview

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:52.230 align:middle line:84%
that Carl Jung went to
see the Raman Maharshi,

00:01:52.230 --> 00:01:53.605 align:middle line:90%
and no words were uttered.

00:01:53.605 --> 00:01:54.840 align:middle line:90%


00:01:54.840 --> 00:02:02.340 align:middle line:84%
And then he said he was in
a profoundly altered state

00:02:02.340 --> 00:02:03.260 align:middle line:90%
of consciousness.

00:02:03.260 --> 00:02:04.290 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: By being
in the presence?

00:02:04.290 --> 00:02:05.748 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: By being
in the presence.

00:02:05.748 --> 00:02:06.870 align:middle line:90%


00:02:06.870 --> 00:02:10.429 align:middle line:84%
So you can make the
person's kundalini to rise.

00:02:10.429 --> 00:02:11.970 align:middle line:90%


00:02:11.970 --> 00:02:19.440 align:middle line:84%
When I move this, I
can catch the kundalini

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:20.500 align:middle line:90%
and then raise it.

00:02:20.500 --> 00:02:25.270 align:middle line:90%


00:02:25.270 --> 00:02:26.700 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes, you can.

00:02:26.700 --> 00:02:30.854 align:middle line:90%


