[CHUCKLING]

00:02:31.354 --> 00:02:33.250 align:middle line:90%


00:02:33.250 --> 00:02:33.970 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:02:33.970 --> 00:02:35.060 align:middle line:90%


00:02:35.060 --> 00:02:36.915 align:middle line:90%
By the power of your intention?

00:02:36.915 --> 00:02:39.290 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah, by the
power of my intention.

00:02:39.290 --> 00:02:40.540 align:middle line:90%


00:02:40.540 --> 00:02:45.620 align:middle line:84%
It depends on certain
conditions, the receptivity

00:02:45.620 --> 00:02:49.270 align:middle line:84%
of the student, and
the student's level

00:02:49.270 --> 00:02:52.405 align:middle line:84%
of consciousness, and
also the teacher's level.

00:02:52.405 --> 00:02:53.940 align:middle line:90%


00:02:53.940 --> 00:02:58.920 align:middle line:84%
So that is important to
take into consideration.

00:02:58.920 --> 00:03:03.070 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I read once
that it's essentially

00:03:03.070 --> 00:03:05.790 align:middle line:90%
