00:03:05.790 --> 00:03:07.660 align:middle line:84%
Do you know what
I'm talking about,

00:03:07.660 --> 00:03:11.970 align:middle line:84%
where it's like a seed
of energy that you're

00:03:11.970 --> 00:03:14.440 align:middle line:84%
transplanting into
the other person?

00:03:14.440 --> 00:03:16.630 align:middle line:84%
Could you explain
that a little more?

00:03:16.630 --> 00:03:17.940 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: It's my intention--

00:03:17.940 --> 00:03:18.940 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's the seed.

00:03:18.940 --> 00:03:19.440 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:21.620 align:middle line:90%


00:03:21.620 --> 00:03:24.980 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: --to impact
the other person,

00:03:24.980 --> 00:03:27.880 align:middle line:84%
to open up his or
her consciousness.

00:03:27.880 --> 00:03:29.790 align:middle line:90%


00:03:29.790 --> 00:03:31.840 align:middle line:84%
And also the raising
of the kundalini.

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:33.400 align:middle line:90%


00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:37.320 align:middle line:84%
The kundalini is the energy
that stays in sixth chakra,

00:03:37.320 --> 00:03:38.840 align:middle line:90%
and below it too.

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:43.992 align:middle line:84%
And when I raise it,
and I bring it up,

00:03:43.992 --> 00:03:48.552 align:middle line:84%
bring it up, and then go
to the third eye, and then

00:03:48.552 --> 00:03:49.260 align:middle line:90%
the crown chakra.

00:03:49.260 --> 00:03:52.330 align:middle line:90%


00:03:52.330 --> 00:03:55.070 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That gives me energy.

00:03:55.070 --> 00:03:57.250 align:middle line:90%
Energy, it lifts the energy.

00:03:57.250 --> 00:04:00.020 align:middle line:84%
Can you do this with
groups of people?

00:04:00.020 --> 00:04:00.840 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah.

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:02.214 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: In mass
groups of people.

00:04:02.214 --> 00:04:04.040 align:middle line:90%


00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:06.410 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah, I've
done that many things.

00:04:06.410 --> 00:04:12.890 align:middle line:84%
