on one of the YouTubes.

00:04:12.890 --> 00:04:15.749 align:middle line:84%
There is a YouTube
called Particle Darshan.

00:04:15.749 --> 00:04:17.432 align:middle line:90%


00:04:17.432 --> 00:04:18.515 align:middle line:90%
Darshan also is Shaktipat.

00:04:18.515 --> 00:04:19.821 align:middle line:90%


00:04:19.821 --> 00:04:21.279 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: What is
that word, Darshan?

00:04:21.279 --> 00:04:22.403 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Particle Darshan.

00:04:22.403 --> 00:04:24.910 align:middle line:90%


00:04:24.910 --> 00:04:25.595 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:04:25.595 --> 00:04:28.200 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: So then people
keep on looking at me.

00:04:28.200 --> 00:04:29.585 align:middle line:90%
Then my eyes will change.

00:04:29.585 --> 00:04:31.300 align:middle line:90%


00:04:31.300 --> 00:04:33.927 align:middle line:84%
