it on the camera.

00:04:33.927 --> 00:04:34.760 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Interesting.

00:04:34.760 --> 00:04:36.120 align:middle line:90%


00:04:36.120 --> 00:04:39.670 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: So you just
watch that particular--

00:04:39.670 --> 00:04:41.430 align:middle line:90%
it's about a minute or two.

00:04:41.430 --> 00:04:42.770 align:middle line:90%
I don't remember.

00:04:42.770 --> 00:04:43.450 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Really?

00:04:43.450 --> 00:04:45.860 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah people have
to only focus on that.

00:04:45.860 --> 00:04:47.780 align:middle line:90%
It is on my YouTube videos.

00:04:47.780 --> 00:04:48.831 align:middle line:90%


00:04:48.831 --> 00:04:50.330 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Where your
eyes will change?

00:04:50.330 --> 00:04:51.964 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah, my
eyes will change.

00:04:51.964 --> 00:04:52.630 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK, so--

00:04:52.630 --> 00:04:54.580 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Then I will not move.

00:04:54.580 --> 00:06:39.770 align:middle line:90%


00:06:39.770 --> 00:06:44.460 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So in this video,
your eyes changed shape?

00:06:44.460 --> 00:06:45.870 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah.

00:06:45.870 --> 00:06:49.640 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And you do that by
slowing down the REM movement

00:06:49.640 --> 00:06:50.860 align:middle line:90%
in your eyes?

00:06:50.860 --> 00:06:52.360 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: I am completely still.

00:06:52.360 --> 00:06:54.391 align:middle line:90%
No words are spoken.

00:06:54.391 --> 00:06:55.890 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And you've
trained yourself?

00:06:55.890 --> 00:06:58.800 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: And then I ask
people to look at me.

00:06:58.800 --> 00:07:00.810 align:middle line:84%
I don't remember even
if I ask them to do it.

00:07:00.810 --> 00:07:04.360 align:middle line:84%
Maybe in the beginning, I
say, this is Particle Darshan.

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:05.840 align:middle line:90%
And it was a while ago.

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:07.130 align:middle line:90%
So I don't remember.

00:07:07.130 --> 00:07:08.289 align:middle line:90%
But there is one.

00:07:08.289 --> 00:07:10.330 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Is that a good
way to start a meditation,

00:07:10.330 --> 00:07:13.770 align:middle line:84%
to be able to slow
the thoughts down

00:07:13.770 --> 00:07:15.230 align:middle line:84%
by stopping the
rapid eye movement?

00:07:15.230 --> 00:07:16.364 align:middle line:90%


00:07:16.364 --> 00:07:18.780 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah, you could keep
your eyes completely still,

00:07:18.780 --> 00:07:21.710 align:middle line:84%
no thoughts will
come to the brain.

00:07:21.710 --> 00:07:24.529 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: How long did it take you
to learn something like that?

00:07:24.529 --> 00:07:26.070 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: In my
case, many lifetimes.

00:07:26.070 --> 00:07:28.800 align:middle line:90%


00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:33.330 align:middle line:84%
So I was born with that
ability to do that.

00:07:33.330 --> 00:07:35.360 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And your
teachers, did they

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:38.912 align:middle line:84%
tell you that you are here
to make major changes?

00:07:38.912 --> 00:07:39.495 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yes.

00:07:39.495 --> 00:07:40.650 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Explain that to me.

00:07:40.650 --> 00:07:42.190 align:middle line:90%


00:07:42.190 --> 00:07:48.170 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Well, in India--
it's a magical country.

00:07:48.170 --> 00:07:50.530 align:middle line:90%
You could just go to India.

00:07:50.530 --> 00:07:53.670 align:middle line:90%


00:07:53.670 --> 00:07:56.050 align:middle line:84%
You can go to my
ashram, for instance.

00:07:56.050 --> 00:07:57.620 align:middle line:90%


00:07:57.620 --> 00:08:00.100 align:middle line:84%
And then they will-- you
just give your thumbprint.

00:08:00.100 --> 00:08:01.910 align:middle line:90%


00:08:01.910 --> 00:08:02.855 align:middle line:90%
Nothing is asked.

00:08:02.855 --> 00:08:03.870 align:middle line:90%


00:08:03.870 --> 00:08:08.220 align:middle line:84%
Then there are scriptures there,
written thousands of years ago.

00:08:08.220 --> 00:08:09.750 align:middle line:90%


00:08:09.750 --> 00:08:12.410 align:middle line:84%
And from that,
they will find out

00:08:12.410 --> 00:08:17.000 align:middle line:84%
your name, your father's
name, your mother's name.

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:18.720 align:middle line:84%
And if you're married,
your husband's

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:21.500 align:middle line:84%
name, and what you are
doing for a living,

00:08:21.500 --> 00:08:22.735 align:middle line:90%
and why you are suffering.

00:08:22.735 --> 00:08:23.770 align:middle line:90%


00:08:23.770 --> 00:08:25.230 align:middle line:90%
All these things will be there.

00:08:25.230 --> 00:08:26.890 align:middle line:90%


00:08:26.890 --> 00:08:30.560 align:middle line:84%
They won't know
anything about you.

00:08:30.560 --> 00:08:32.049 align:middle line:90%


00:08:32.049 --> 00:08:34.240 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And I could do
this not being from India?

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:36.528 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah, you can
do it on Skype also.

00:08:36.528 --> 00:08:37.600 align:middle line:90%


00:08:37.600 --> 00:08:39.080 align:middle line:90%
I just introduced that.

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:39.868 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What?

00:08:39.868 --> 00:08:41.409 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: You can
do it on the Skype.

00:08:41.409 --> 00:08:43.860 align:middle line:90%


00:08:43.860 --> 00:08:45.060 align:middle line:90%
It is called astroved.com.

00:08:45.060 --> 00:08:46.520 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What is it?

00:08:46.520 --> 00:08:47.478 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Astroved.com.

00:08:47.478 --> 00:08:50.850 align:middle line:90%


00:08:50.850 --> 00:08:55.420 align:middle line:84%
All that you need to do
is you just send your--

00:08:55.420 --> 00:08:57.255 align:middle line:84%
if you are a woman,
left thumbprint.

00:08:57.255 --> 00:08:59.370 align:middle line:84%
If you are a man,
the right thumbprint.

00:08:59.370 --> 00:09:00.495 align:middle line:90%


00:09:00.495 --> 00:09:03.012 align:middle line:84%
You just scan it, and
then send it to them.

00:09:03.012 --> 00:09:04.595 align:middle line:84%
And then they will
set an appointment.

00:09:04.595 --> 00:09:07.155 align:middle line:90%


00:09:07.155 --> 00:09:09.320 align:middle line:84%
And only certain
people can do that

00:09:09.320 --> 00:09:10.585 align:middle line:90%
who are born in that family.

00:09:10.585 --> 00:09:11.640 align:middle line:90%


00:09:11.640 --> 00:09:15.770 align:middle line:84%
And they have the
leaves, palm leaves,

00:09:15.770 --> 00:09:18.600 align:middle line:84%
on which everything
was written to you.

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:19.925 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh my goodness!

00:09:19.925 --> 00:09:23.440 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: In a very
coded language.

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:24.326 align:middle line:90%
So they will come.

00:09:24.326 --> 00:09:25.450 align:middle line:90%
And then they will ask you.

00:09:25.450 --> 00:09:32.680 align:middle line:84%
Now, I once had in
New York 500 people

00:09:32.680 --> 00:09:33.930 align:middle line:90%
watching this on the video.

00:09:33.930 --> 00:09:36.275 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Oh my goodness,
watching it live?

00:09:36.275 --> 00:09:37.400 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Watching it live.

00:09:37.400 --> 00:09:39.537 align:middle line:84%
I can do it for
you on a show, too.

00:09:39.537 --> 00:09:40.370 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Interesting.

00:09:40.370 --> 00:09:41.640 align:middle line:90%


00:09:41.640 --> 00:09:42.314 align:middle line:90%
And now--

00:09:42.314 --> 00:09:43.480 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Anybody can do it.

00:09:43.480 --> 00:09:46.710 align:middle line:90%
I don't have to be present.

00:09:46.710 --> 00:09:49.280 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And why the
left finger-- thumb

00:09:49.280 --> 00:09:50.780 align:middle line:84%
for the woman and
right for the man?

00:09:50.780 --> 00:09:51.510 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: I don't know why.

00:09:51.510 --> 00:09:52.500 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: You don't know?

00:09:52.500 --> 00:09:55.640 align:middle line:84%
And this is a family, a
lineage of family members

00:09:55.640 --> 00:09:56.510 align:middle line:90%
that have this gift?

00:09:56.510 --> 00:09:58.700 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: There
about maybe totally

00:09:58.700 --> 00:10:02.080 align:middle line:84%
about less than 200
people who can do that.

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:02.967 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:10:02.967 --> 00:10:03.800 align:middle line:90%
Are you one of them?

00:10:03.800 --> 00:10:05.595 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: No, I'm not.

00:10:05.595 --> 00:10:07.954 align:middle line:84%
