who work for me.

00:10:07.954 --> 00:10:08.870 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: In the ashram?

00:10:08.870 --> 00:10:10.225 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: In the ashram, yeah.

00:10:10.225 --> 00:10:11.070 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:10:11.070 --> 00:10:13.185 align:middle line:84%
What is your ashram
called in India?

00:10:13.185 --> 00:10:15.530 align:middle line:90%


