rendered through two websites.

00:10:29.445 --> 00:10:30.610 align:middle line:90%


00:10:30.610 --> 00:10:31.610 align:middle line:90%
One is pillaicenter.com.

00:10:31.610 --> 00:10:33.260 align:middle line:90%


00:10:33.260 --> 00:10:35.802 align:middle line:90%
And the other is astroved.com

00:10:35.802 --> 00:10:42.300 align:middle line:84%
Because I don't believe in
opening my esoteric teachings

00:10:42.300 --> 00:10:43.550 align:middle line:90%
