So it's a closed setting.

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:50.880 align:middle line:90%


00:10:50.880 --> 00:10:53.300 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And why is
your choice for that?

00:10:53.300 --> 00:10:55.192 align:middle line:84%
What is your choice
in doing that?

00:10:55.192 --> 00:10:57.150 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: It's because
people have to be ready.

00:10:57.150 --> 00:10:59.510 align:middle line:90%


00:10:59.510 --> 00:11:02.980 align:middle line:84%
And it's not, you know, like, I
truly believe Jesus is saying,

00:11:02.980 --> 00:11:05.290 align:middle line:84%
don't throw the pearls
before the swines.

00:11:05.290 --> 00:11:06.480 align:middle line:90%


00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:08.220 align:middle line:90%
It's a waste of time.

00:11:08.220 --> 00:11:08.720 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:10.210 align:middle line:90%


00:11:10.210 --> 00:11:14.790 align:middle line:84%
In your experience as
a spiritual teacher,

00:11:14.790 --> 00:11:16.900 align:middle line:84%
do you find that
there are people

00:11:16.900 --> 00:11:21.250 align:middle line:84%
that will follow you
and only follow you

00:11:21.250 --> 00:11:23.422 align:middle line:84%
without going on and
living their lives?

00:11:23.422 --> 00:11:25.130 align:middle line:84%
That they will just
dedicate themselves--

00:11:25.130 --> 00:11:28.380 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: No, my
teaching is 200% life.

00:11:28.380 --> 00:11:29.440 align:middle line:90%


00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:30.425 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Explain.

00:11:30.425 --> 00:11:32.940 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: 100% material
and 100% spiritual.

00:11:32.940 --> 00:11:34.770 align:middle line:90%


00:11:34.770 --> 00:11:41.649 align:middle line:84%
You don't have to leave
your profession or business

00:11:41.649 --> 00:11:44.065 align:middle line:84%
or anything that you are doing
in order to be enlightened.

00:11:44.065 --> 00:11:46.910 align:middle line:90%


00:11:46.910 --> 00:11:48.500 align:middle line:84%
You can do everything
that you want

00:11:48.500 --> 00:11:52.515 align:middle line:90%
to do and still be enlightened.

00:11:52.515 --> 00:11:54.950 align:middle line:90%


00:11:54.950 --> 00:11:57.350 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, it's just
a lopsided reality.

00:11:57.350 --> 00:11:59.340 align:middle line:90%
Look at the Buddha's reality.

00:11:59.340 --> 00:12:01.200 align:middle line:84%
The Buddha could
have been a king.

00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:04.320 align:middle line:84%
He was the only
heir to the throne.

00:12:04.320 --> 00:12:07.240 align:middle line:84%
But he elected to become
an ascetic and a recluse.

00:12:07.240 --> 00:12:09.370 align:middle line:90%


00:12:09.370 --> 00:12:12.694 align:middle line:84%
That is not a model
agreeable to me.

00:12:12.694 --> 00:12:14.110 align:middle line:84%
But I'm not
condemning the Buddha.

00:12:14.110 --> 00:12:16.040 align:middle line:90%
He's a great being.

00:12:16.040 --> 00:12:18.110 align:middle line:90%
But that's what he chose to do.

00:12:18.110 --> 00:12:23.385 align:middle line:84%
He chose to leave his wife,
his son, and his father

00:12:23.385 --> 00:12:23.995 align:middle line:90%
and kingdom.

00:12:23.995 --> 00:12:26.170 align:middle line:90%


00:12:26.170 --> 00:12:29.340 align:middle line:84%
But my model is that you
can do it both together.

00:12:29.340 --> 00:12:30.650 align:middle line:90%
That is my lineage.

00:12:30.650 --> 00:12:34.290 align:middle line:84%
My lineage, all the Siddhas,
we are married people.

00:12:34.290 --> 00:12:35.890 align:middle line:90%
And then they live this life.

00:12:35.890 --> 00:12:38.630 align:middle line:84%
And then they will
also simultaneously

00:12:38.630 --> 00:12:40.670 align:middle line:90%
live the other world, too.

00:12:40.670 --> 00:12:43.040 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And you're still
in constant contact

00:12:43.040 --> 00:12:45.540 align:middle line:90%
with your wife and your child?

00:12:45.540 --> 00:12:46.590 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Of course.

00:12:46.590 --> 00:12:49.390 align:middle line:84%
I have a daughter who
is grown up and married.

00:12:49.390 --> 00:12:51.520 align:middle line:90%


00:12:51.520 --> 00:12:53.990 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And did she go on to
study your tradition as well?

00:12:53.990 --> 00:12:57.260 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Well, she's a
professor in a law school.

00:12:57.260 --> 00:12:58.990 align:middle line:90%
So she does her thing.

00:12:58.990 --> 00:13:00.785 align:middle line:90%
But she is spiritual, too.

00:13:00.785 --> 00:13:01.349 align:middle line:90%


00:13:01.349 --> 00:13:02.390 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's wonderful.

00:13:02.390 --> 00:13:03.450 align:middle line:90%


00:13:03.450 --> 00:13:05.800 align:middle line:90%
What is your overarching goal?

00:13:05.800 --> 00:13:08.150 align:middle line:90%
What did you come here to do?

00:13:08.150 --> 00:13:11.390 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: I just came here
to do to prove to the world

00:13:11.390 --> 00:13:20.090 align:middle line:84%
that through changing your
mindset, or consciousness,

00:13:20.090 --> 00:13:24.900 align:middle line:84%
which is basically changing
how the brain works,

00:13:24.900 --> 00:13:29.105 align:middle line:84%
you can change anything
that you want to change.

00:13:29.105 --> 00:13:31.520 align:middle line:90%


00:13:31.520 --> 00:13:33.290 align:middle line:90%
You can heal your body.

00:13:33.290 --> 00:13:34.580 align:middle line:90%


00:13:34.580 --> 00:13:36.570 align:middle line:90%
You can change your finances.

00:13:36.570 --> 00:13:38.200 align:middle line:84%
You can also fix
your relationships.

00:13:38.200 --> 00:13:39.260 align:middle line:90%


00:13:39.260 --> 00:13:41.850 align:middle line:84%
All these things, these are
the major areas of human life.

00:13:41.850 --> 00:13:43.977 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But you have to
want it first, don't you?

00:13:43.977 --> 00:13:44.810 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Of course.

00:13:44.810 --> 00:13:48.610 align:middle line:84%
If you don't want it first,
then nothing can be done.

00:13:48.610 --> 00:13:50.620 align:middle line:84%
Because it's a choice
that people make.

00:13:50.620 --> 00:13:52.380 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But sometimes people
don't know what they want.

00:13:52.380 --> 00:13:54.439 align:middle line:84%
As you said, they don't
have any prior knowledge.

00:13:54.439 --> 00:13:55.980 align:middle line:84%
They're just living
in the suffering.

00:13:55.980 --> 00:13:59.310 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: But everybody
wants a nice home.

00:13:59.310 --> 00:14:05.570 align:middle line:84%
Everybody wants a little bit
of cash for them to spend.

00:14:05.570 --> 00:14:07.800 align:middle line:84%
And everybody wants
a good relationship.

00:14:07.800 --> 00:14:11.065 align:middle line:84%
And if they don't want
it, then it's difficult.

00:14:11.065 --> 00:14:12.890 align:middle line:90%


00:14:12.890 --> 00:14:14.770 align:middle line:90%
They have to want it.

00:14:14.770 --> 00:14:16.390 align:middle line:90%
They have the want.

00:14:16.390 --> 00:14:19.010 align:middle line:84%
And I think that's not a
big deal, because everybody,

00:14:19.010 --> 00:14:22.230 align:middle line:84%
if you ask anybody, do you
want to live in poverty,

00:14:22.230 --> 00:14:23.940 align:middle line:84%
or do you want to
live in abundance?

00:14:23.940 --> 00:14:26.690 align:middle line:84%
Everybody's going to say, no,
I just want a Rolls Royce.

00:14:26.690 --> 00:14:28.120 align:middle line:90%
I want a Ferrari.

00:14:28.120 --> 00:14:32.220 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Of course, well--
well-- in your case,

00:14:32.220 --> 00:14:34.900 align:middle line:84%
when you say that you want to
prove to people that they can

00:14:34.900 --> 00:14:38.010 align:middle line:84%
use the power of their
mind to manifest,

00:14:38.010 --> 00:14:40.430 align:middle line:84%
what happens if
that doesn't happen?

00:14:40.430 --> 00:14:41.580 align:middle line:90%


00:14:41.580 --> 00:14:42.480 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Keep doing.

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:43.530 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Keep doing it?

00:14:43.530 --> 00:14:45.020 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah, keep doing.

00:14:45.020 --> 00:14:46.310 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And so far--

00:14:46.310 --> 00:14:47.726 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah,
that's what it is.

00:14:47.726 --> 00:14:50.430 align:middle line:84%
This question was asked-- was
put to Paramahansa Yogananda.

00:14:50.430 --> 00:14:51.485 align:middle line:90%


00:14:51.485 --> 00:14:52.370 align:middle line:90%
He lived here.

00:14:52.370 --> 00:14:55.195 align:middle line:84%
And he also passed
away in Los Angeles.

00:14:55.195 --> 00:14:56.466 align:middle line:90%


00:14:56.466 --> 00:14:59.100 align:middle line:84%
You have heard about this
man, Paramahansa Yogananda?

00:14:59.100 --> 00:15:00.350 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Of course.

00:15:00.350 --> 00:15:03.600 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Who wrote the book,
"The Autobiography of a Yogi."

00:15:03.600 --> 00:15:05.220 align:middle line:90%
His main center is in Watts.

00:15:05.220 --> 00:15:07.350 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I've interviewed
many from his center.

00:15:07.350 --> 00:15:07.850 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:15:07.850 --> 00:15:09.700 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: In this
city is the building

00:15:09.700 --> 00:15:12.760 align:middle line:84%
that he first bought
in Mount Washington.

00:15:12.760 --> 00:15:13.830 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Mhm.

00:15:13.830 --> 00:15:18.780 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: His guru came and
told him the previous night,

00:15:18.780 --> 00:15:21.120 align:middle line:84%
there is a building
waiting for you.

00:15:21.120 --> 00:15:22.930 align:middle line:90%
Go get it.

00:15:22.930 --> 00:15:26.920 align:middle line:84%
That was the only building
where the Hollywood stars were

00:15:26.920 --> 00:15:29.290 align:middle line:84%
staying at that time because
there were no five star

00:15:29.290 --> 00:15:30.230 align:middle line:90%
hotels at that time.

00:15:30.230 --> 00:15:31.650 align:middle line:90%


00:15:31.650 --> 00:15:33.450 align:middle line:90%
The guru had come and told him.

00:15:33.450 --> 00:15:36.740 align:middle line:84%
By the time Paramahansa
had come here,

00:15:36.740 --> 00:15:39.340 align:middle line:84%
had no visa, nothing,
there was a woman

00:15:39.340 --> 00:15:42.570 align:middle line:84%
was driving him around
and telling him,

00:15:42.570 --> 00:15:43.780 align:middle line:90%
what are you looking for?

00:15:43.780 --> 00:15:45.100 align:middle line:90%


00:15:45.100 --> 00:15:48.720 align:middle line:84%
I'm looking for the building
that my guru had shown me

00:15:48.720 --> 00:15:49.330 align:middle line:90%
in a dream.

00:15:49.330 --> 00:15:50.625 align:middle line:90%


00:15:50.625 --> 00:15:51.500 align:middle line:90%
What do you thinking?

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:54.115 align:middle line:90%
This is a really posh area.

00:15:54.115 --> 00:15:56.600 align:middle line:90%


00:15:56.600 --> 00:15:58.710 align:middle line:90%
Are you in your mind?

00:15:58.710 --> 00:16:01.656 align:middle line:84%
He said, I am not in
my mind, of course.

00:16:01.656 --> 00:16:03.350 align:middle line:90%


00:16:03.350 --> 00:16:07.640 align:middle line:84%
So when he came to this
building, he said stop.

00:16:07.640 --> 00:16:09.135 align:middle line:84%
This is the building
I want to buy.

00:16:09.135 --> 00:16:10.660 align:middle line:90%


00:16:10.660 --> 00:16:12.200 align:middle line:84%
You can go and look
at the building.

00:16:12.200 --> 00:16:15.330 align:middle line:84%
It was used to play tennis
and everything there

00:16:15.330 --> 00:16:16.055 align:middle line:90%
in that building.

00:16:16.055 --> 00:16:17.310 align:middle line:90%


00:16:17.310 --> 00:16:19.690 align:middle line:84%
It was gorgeous, gorgeous
building with a lot of land.

00:16:19.690 --> 00:16:21.230 align:middle line:90%


00:16:21.230 --> 00:16:28.500 align:middle line:84%
And he had no money, literally
no money to buy that building.

00:16:28.500 --> 00:16:30.650 align:middle line:90%
So the lady-- he bought it.

00:16:30.650 --> 00:16:32.170 align:middle line:90%
And it's a long story.

00:16:32.170 --> 00:16:32.670 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: How?

00:16:32.670 --> 00:16:33.730 align:middle line:90%


00:16:33.730 --> 00:16:37.410 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Well,
he asked the lady

00:16:37.410 --> 00:16:39.820 align:middle line:84%
to stop the car to find
out if it is for sale.

00:16:39.820 --> 00:16:41.660 align:middle line:84%
She came back and
said, it is for sale.

00:16:41.660 --> 00:16:43.450 align:middle line:90%
Then I will buy it.

00:16:43.450 --> 00:16:44.570 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:16:44.570 --> 00:16:45.730 align:middle line:90%
And how did he do it?

00:16:45.730 --> 00:16:47.551 align:middle line:90%


00:16:47.551 --> 00:16:49.230 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: He used
to heal people.

00:16:49.230 --> 00:16:50.630 align:middle line:90%


00:16:50.630 --> 00:16:52.370 align:middle line:90%
So he healed some rich people.

00:16:52.370 --> 00:16:53.310 align:middle line:90%
And some money came.

00:16:53.310 --> 00:16:57.550 align:middle line:90%
At that time, it was $40,000.

00:16:57.550 --> 00:16:59.960 align:middle line:84%
Today, it would be like-- that
building will be like $10,

00:16:59.960 --> 00:17:00.550 align:middle line:90%
$20 million.

00:17:00.550 --> 00:17:04.680 align:middle line:90%


00:17:04.680 --> 00:17:06.570 align:middle line:90%
And there were challenges.

00:17:06.570 --> 00:17:11.750 align:middle line:84%
And then he had--
Of course, the house

00:17:11.750 --> 00:17:17.516 align:middle line:84%
was in like a 90 day--
what do they call?

00:17:17.516 --> 00:17:18.140 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Escrow?

00:17:18.140 --> 00:17:20.574 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Escrow, 90 day escrow.

00:17:20.574 --> 00:17:22.119 align:middle line:90%
Time was running out.

00:17:22.119 --> 00:17:25.910 align:middle line:90%
He could not get the $5,000.

00:17:25.910 --> 00:17:26.910 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: The last $5,000?

00:17:26.910 --> 00:17:30.740 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: The last,
$35,000 he was able to pay.

00:17:30.740 --> 00:17:34.360 align:middle line:84%
And then the $5,000 was
really a big problem.

00:17:34.360 --> 00:17:39.420 align:middle line:84%
But at the time, he called--
a woman called from Boston.

00:17:39.420 --> 00:17:41.200 align:middle line:90%
I have the $5,000.

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:44.010 align:middle line:84%
But I have to drive from
Boston to Los Angeles.

00:17:44.010 --> 00:17:45.310 align:middle line:90%


00:17:45.310 --> 00:17:46.684 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: To give it to you.

00:17:46.684 --> 00:17:47.850 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: To give it to you.

00:17:47.850 --> 00:17:49.950 align:middle line:90%
But then you'll run out of time.

00:17:49.950 --> 00:17:51.040 align:middle line:90%
But he called the owner.

00:17:51.040 --> 00:17:54.800 align:middle line:84%
The owner said, I want to
give it to you, regardless.

00:17:54.800 --> 00:17:58.330 align:middle line:84%
Although I have a better offer,
but I don't want to do that.

00:17:58.330 --> 00:18:01.420 align:middle line:90%
I want my building to go to you.

00:18:01.420 --> 00:18:04.340 align:middle line:84%
And he-- this is the
most important point.

00:18:04.340 --> 00:18:08.350 align:middle line:84%
The lady who was
driving him asked him,

00:18:08.350 --> 00:18:09.970 align:middle line:90%
how did you manage to do this?

00:18:09.970 --> 00:18:11.490 align:middle line:90%
Because I believed in it.

00:18:11.490 --> 00:18:13.112 align:middle line:90%
And you didn't believe in it.

00:18:13.112 --> 00:18:15.440 align:middle line:90%


00:18:15.440 --> 00:18:19.460 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's an amazing
lesson in-- where people believe

00:18:19.460 --> 00:18:22.650 align:middle line:84%
in something, and
somebody else doesn't.

00:18:22.650 --> 00:18:24.695 align:middle line:84%
Who is responsible
for making it happen?

00:18:24.695 --> 00:18:26.786 align:middle line:90%


00:18:26.786 --> 00:18:30.150 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: That happens most
of the time between couples.

00:18:30.150 --> 00:18:35.620 align:middle line:84%
It's really ironic
and painful, too.

00:18:35.620 --> 00:18:38.540 align:middle line:90%


00:18:38.540 --> 00:18:43.730 align:middle line:84%
That the husband usually
is a left brain person

00:18:43.730 --> 00:18:47.080 align:middle line:84%
and doesn't-- you know,
you are off the wall.

00:18:47.080 --> 00:18:48.320 align:middle line:90%
And you are a dreamer.

00:18:48.320 --> 00:18:50.450 align:middle line:90%


00:18:50.450 --> 00:18:52.200 align:middle line:84%
I have so many
students like that.

00:18:52.200 --> 00:18:55.360 align:middle line:84%
I am the only one who
has to make the money.

00:18:55.360 --> 00:18:58.550 align:middle line:90%
And you are a new age crackpot.

00:18:58.550 --> 00:19:01.940 align:middle line:90%


00:19:01.940 --> 00:19:04.430 align:middle line:84%
These things are
not going to happen.

00:19:04.430 --> 00:19:07.860 align:middle line:90%
So that's really difficult.

00:19:07.860 --> 00:19:11.470 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Could the new age
person intend it or will it?

00:19:11.470 --> 00:19:13.430 align:middle line:84%
Or when you have
somebody who doesn't

00:19:13.430 --> 00:19:17.220 align:middle line:84%
have the same intentions,
can you really manifest it?

00:19:17.220 --> 00:19:20.064 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: It is very difficult
if they live in the same space.

00:19:20.064 --> 00:19:21.730 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Or if you
want to have something

00:19:21.730 --> 00:19:22.688 align:middle line:90%
to do with that person.

00:19:22.688 --> 00:19:23.750 align:middle line:90%


00:19:23.750 --> 00:19:26.124 align:middle line:84%
So is it better to
manifest on your own?

00:19:26.124 --> 00:19:27.040 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: On your own.

00:19:27.040 --> 00:19:28.200 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: On your own.

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:29.846 align:middle line:84%
Could groups manifest
together as long

00:19:29.846 --> 00:19:31.020 align:middle line:90%
as they have the same intention?

00:19:31.020 --> 00:19:31.645 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah.

00:19:31.645 --> 00:19:32.970 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Is it more effective?

00:19:32.970 --> 00:19:35.030 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: It is effective
they are in a group.

00:19:35.030 --> 00:19:35.913 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: In a group?

00:19:35.913 --> 00:19:37.090 align:middle line:90%
So--

00:19:37.090 --> 00:19:39.180 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: And they
have to prove also.

00:19:39.180 --> 00:19:40.410 align:middle line:90%
They have to prove also.

00:19:40.410 --> 00:19:41.493 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: They have to what?

00:19:41.493 --> 00:19:44.020 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Prove that they
are able to manifest.

00:19:44.020 --> 00:19:45.320 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I see.

00:19:45.320 --> 00:19:48.230 align:middle line:84%
So if someone were
to-- say two children

00:19:48.230 --> 00:19:51.830 align:middle line:84%
were to intend the well being
of a parent who is dying.

00:19:51.830 --> 00:19:53.140 align:middle line:90%


00:19:53.140 --> 00:19:56.930 align:middle line:84%
Does the parent also want
to have the will to live?

00:19:56.930 --> 00:19:59.795 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: It will
be helpful if they

00:19:59.795 --> 00:20:01.300 align:middle line:90%
are both on the same wavelength.

00:20:01.300 --> 00:20:02.890 align:middle line:90%


00:20:02.890 --> 00:20:03.870 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Interesting.

00:20:03.870 --> 00:20:05.960 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: If they are
not, it is difficult.

00:20:05.960 --> 00:20:07.470 align:middle line:90%
But it still can be done.

00:20:07.470 --> 00:20:08.900 align:middle line:84%
It depends upon
the consciousness

00:20:08.900 --> 00:20:11.400 align:middle line:90%
of this person who is intending.

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:12.600 align:middle line:90%


00:20:12.600 --> 00:20:14.060 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So in your
desire of what

00:20:14.060 --> 00:20:16.030 align:middle line:84%
you want to do, in
terms of teach people

00:20:16.030 --> 00:20:17.130 align:middle line:90%
that they can create.

00:20:17.130 --> 00:20:20.480 align:middle line:84%
And I could ask you questions
about this all day long.

00:20:20.480 --> 00:20:22.505 align:middle line:90%
What have you experienced?

00:20:22.505 --> 00:20:23.570 align:middle line:90%


00:20:23.570 --> 00:20:24.940 align:middle line:90%
Are people learning this?

00:20:24.940 --> 00:20:25.857 align:middle line:90%
Are they receiving it?

00:20:25.857 --> 00:20:26.898 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah, they are.

00:20:26.898 --> 00:20:27.660 align:middle line:90%
They are.

00:20:27.660 --> 00:20:29.150 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: More than ever now?

00:20:29.150 --> 00:20:31.520 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah,
definitely they are.

00:20:31.520 --> 00:20:33.610 align:middle line:84%
The world is changing,
definitely changing.

00:20:33.610 --> 00:20:35.610 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's what I
want to talk to you about.

00:20:35.610 --> 00:20:37.330 align:middle line:84%
So when you say it's
changing, how long

00:20:37.330 --> 00:20:39.180 align:middle line:84%
have you seen this
change coming about?

00:20:39.180 --> 00:20:43.370 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: I think it has
made a dramatic shift

00:20:43.370 --> 00:20:47.330 align:middle line:90%
beginning of the 2012.

00:20:47.330 --> 00:20:49.810 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Do you feel that
there are dark forces?

00:20:49.810 --> 00:20:51.160 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: The last of the
Mayan calendar in the--

00:20:51.160 --> 00:20:51.951 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Well, yeah.

00:20:51.951 --> 00:20:54.300 align:middle line:84%
Do you feel that there are
still dark forces present?

00:20:54.300 --> 00:20:56.780 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: There will
always be dark forces.

00:20:56.780 --> 00:21:00.150 align:middle line:84%
They will be against the
evolution of the human race.

00:21:00.150 --> 00:21:01.800 align:middle line:90%


00:21:01.800 --> 00:21:03.370 align:middle line:84%
And we have to
fight against them.

00:21:03.370 --> 00:21:05.715 align:middle line:84%
And a large group
of people meditating

00:21:05.715 --> 00:21:07.195 align:middle line:90%
will facilitate the process.

00:21:07.195 --> 00:21:07.514 align:middle line:90%


00:21:07.514 --> 00:21:09.305 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Do you know
something specifically?

00:21:09.305 --> 00:21:10.880 align:middle line:90%


00:21:10.880 --> 00:21:16.735 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: For instance, the
Maharishi's group, about 10,

00:21:16.735 --> 00:21:21.820 align:middle line:84%
12 years ago in Washington,
DC, they brought 3,000 people.

00:21:21.820 --> 00:21:25.140 align:middle line:84%
And then they told the
police department of DC

00:21:25.140 --> 00:21:28.150 align:middle line:84%
that we will bring
down the crime

00:21:28.150 --> 00:21:30.410 align:middle line:90%
rate by 25% in three months.

00:21:30.410 --> 00:21:31.580 align:middle line:90%


00:21:31.580 --> 00:21:36.500 align:middle line:84%
Just 3,000 people sitting
in one place and meditating

00:21:36.500 --> 00:21:40.295 align:middle line:84%
brought down 25% percent of
the crime in Washington, DC.

00:21:40.295 --> 00:21:41.390 align:middle line:90%


00:21:41.390 --> 00:21:42.560 align:middle line:90%
It's a scientific fact.

00:21:42.560 --> 00:21:44.920 align:middle line:90%


00:21:44.920 --> 00:21:49.210 align:middle line:84%
And now the police department
is a partner in the study.

00:21:49.210 --> 00:21:50.730 align:middle line:90%


00:21:50.730 --> 00:21:54.046 align:middle line:84%
So group consciousness
is very, very important.

00:21:54.046 --> 00:21:55.039 align:middle line:90%


00:21:55.039 --> 00:21:55.580 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: How--

00:21:55.580 --> 00:21:56.950 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: I think
if you do something

00:21:56.950 --> 00:21:58.866 align:middle line:84%
like that, that would
be useful for the world.

00:21:58.866 --> 00:22:00.530 align:middle line:90%


00:22:00.530 --> 00:22:02.840 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Are there groups
now all over, right?

00:22:02.840 --> 00:22:04.215 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah,
yeah, the problem

00:22:04.215 --> 00:22:06.610 align:middle line:84%
is every group
thinks that they've

00:22:06.610 --> 00:22:08.025 align:middle line:90%
got the right meditation.

00:22:08.025 --> 00:22:10.015 align:middle line:90%


00:22:10.015 --> 00:22:11.160 align:middle line:90%
That's the problem.

00:22:11.160 --> 00:22:12.950 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Why are we
so divided like that?

00:22:12.950 --> 00:22:14.360 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Because ego.

00:22:14.360 --> 00:22:15.130 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Ego, yes.

00:22:15.130 --> 00:22:17.720 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: It's because of
ego, which is ignorance.

00:22:17.720 --> 00:22:20.060 align:middle line:84%
To me, it doesn't
matter whether it

00:22:20.060 --> 00:22:22.665 align:middle line:84%
is a Muslim group
or a Christian group

00:22:22.665 --> 00:22:26.030 align:middle line:84%
or a Hindu group or
Bahai or whatever group,

00:22:26.030 --> 00:22:27.010 align:middle line:90%
Native American group.

00:22:27.010 --> 00:22:29.430 align:middle line:90%
They all can join together.

00:22:29.430 --> 00:22:30.890 align:middle line:84%
And then let them
do whatever they

00:22:30.890 --> 00:22:33.440 align:middle line:84%
want to do because they
are calling on God.

00:22:33.440 --> 00:22:35.205 align:middle line:84%
And God understands
every language.

00:22:35.205 --> 00:22:36.330 align:middle line:90%


00:22:36.330 --> 00:22:38.300 align:middle line:84%
Of course, there are
techniques to help

00:22:38.300 --> 00:22:40.390 align:middle line:90%
you to get beyond the mind.

00:22:40.390 --> 00:22:43.469 align:middle line:84%
And that can be incorporated
if the tradition doesn't

00:22:43.469 --> 00:22:44.260 align:middle line:90%
have the technique.

00:22:44.260 --> 00:22:45.600 align:middle line:90%


00:22:45.600 --> 00:22:48.160 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Well, the techniques
are, as you talked about

00:22:48.160 --> 00:22:54.070 align:middle line:84%
in the other show, getting past
the ego into a place of bliss.

00:22:54.070 --> 00:22:54.939 align:middle line:90%


00:22:54.939 --> 00:22:56.730 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: The moment
you put your attention

00:22:56.730 --> 00:23:00.170 align:middle line:84%
in the mid-brain, the
attention will go on there.

00:23:00.170 --> 00:23:05.470 align:middle line:84%
Then the frontal lobe, which
is this reality which says I

00:23:05.470 --> 00:23:07.426 align:middle line:90%
am just $10, or $20.

00:23:07.426 --> 00:23:09.010 align:middle line:90%


00:23:09.010 --> 00:23:11.020 align:middle line:90%
And I have a bad relationship.

00:23:11.020 --> 00:23:12.040 align:middle line:90%
I don't look good.

00:23:12.040 --> 00:23:13.530 align:middle line:90%
And then I am overweight.

00:23:13.530 --> 00:23:19.010 align:middle line:84%
All this nonsense, it's
all completely coded here.

00:23:19.010 --> 00:23:23.100 align:middle line:84%
When you just go into
the mid-brain area,

00:23:23.100 --> 00:23:25.720 align:middle line:84%
the mid-brain doesn't
to differentiate

00:23:25.720 --> 00:23:26.995 align:middle line:90%
between reality and illusion.

00:23:26.995 --> 00:23:28.810 align:middle line:90%


00:23:28.810 --> 00:23:30.245 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What about aging?

00:23:30.245 --> 00:23:30.950 align:middle line:90%
Can--

00:23:30.950 --> 00:23:32.770 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Everything,
everything you

00:23:32.770 --> 00:23:34.265 align:middle line:90%
can program in the mid-brain.

00:23:34.265 --> 00:23:35.592 align:middle line:90%


00:23:35.592 --> 00:23:36.300 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What is--

00:23:36.300 --> 00:23:37.676 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: You can
stop the aging.

00:23:37.676 --> 00:23:39.300 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You can stop
the aging process?

00:23:39.300 --> 00:23:41.080 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Stopping
aging is stopping time.

00:23:41.080 --> 00:23:42.038 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: How do you do--

00:23:42.038 --> 00:23:43.427 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Time is aging.

00:23:43.427 --> 00:23:44.010 align:middle line:90%
What is aging?

00:23:44.010 --> 00:23:45.110 align:middle line:90%
Aging is time.

00:23:45.110 --> 00:23:47.010 align:middle line:90%
And time is unreal.

00:23:47.010 --> 00:23:52.800 align:middle line:84%
And if you let go of
this concept of time

00:23:52.800 --> 00:23:56.400 align:middle line:84%
that you have currently,
that's what matters.

00:23:56.400 --> 00:23:57.980 align:middle line:90%


00:23:57.980 --> 00:24:00.227 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Have you let go
of the aging process?

00:24:00.227 --> 00:24:01.060 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Of course.

00:24:01.060 --> 00:24:01.942 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: You did?

00:24:01.942 --> 00:24:02.824 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Of course.

00:24:02.824 --> 00:24:05.750 align:middle line:90%


00:24:05.750 --> 00:24:08.020 align:middle line:90%
I'm 66 years old.

00:24:08.020 --> 00:24:10.590 align:middle line:90%
I just don't feel that I am 66.

00:24:10.590 --> 00:24:14.840 align:middle line:84%
And I always think
that I'm 15-year-old.

00:24:14.840 --> 00:24:15.460 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: 15?

00:24:15.460 --> 00:24:16.876 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah.

00:24:16.876 --> 00:24:17.820 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: [CHUCKLING].

00:24:17.820 --> 00:24:19.240 align:middle line:90%


00:24:19.240 --> 00:24:20.210 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:24:20.210 --> 00:24:22.640 align:middle line:84%
I didn't mean to laugh, I
mean just because it's fun.

00:24:22.640 --> 00:24:23.810 align:middle line:90%


00:24:23.810 --> 00:24:25.120 align:middle line:90%
It's a fun--

00:24:25.120 --> 00:24:27.750 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: The moment you
say, if you re-enforce

00:24:27.750 --> 00:24:30.530 align:middle line:84%
the fact that you
are old, or 65,

00:24:30.530 --> 00:24:32.501 align:middle line:84%
and then your prostate
is going to go wrong.

00:24:32.501 --> 00:24:34.000 align:middle line:84%
And if you go to
the doctor, they'll

00:24:34.000 --> 00:24:35.980 align:middle line:84%
hear-- he'll say,
oh, for your age.

00:24:35.980 --> 00:24:37.610 align:middle line:90%


00:24:37.610 --> 00:24:39.220 align:middle line:84%
This is what I hear
from my doctors.

00:24:39.220 --> 00:24:43.494 align:middle line:84%
For your age, you're
doing well, because these

00:24:43.494 --> 00:24:45.285 align:middle line:84%
are the things that
should have gone wrong.

00:24:45.285 --> 00:24:46.450 align:middle line:90%


00:24:46.450 --> 00:24:49.180 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Interesting, because
you don't go to doctors,

00:24:49.180 --> 00:24:51.350 align:middle line:84%
or because you just
don't believe in that?

00:24:51.350 --> 00:24:52.130 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: I do go.

00:24:52.130 --> 00:24:55.840 align:middle line:84%
I have-- my doctor
is my student also.

00:24:55.840 --> 00:24:57.714 align:middle line:90%
So he knows.

00:24:57.714 --> 00:24:58.630 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: So that helps.

00:24:58.630 --> 00:24:59.740 align:middle line:90%


00:24:59.740 --> 00:25:02.456 align:middle line:84%
The normal statistics
are not placed on you.

00:25:02.456 --> 00:25:03.080 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah.

00:25:03.080 --> 00:25:05.490 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So we've talked
a little bit about money.

00:25:05.490 --> 00:25:07.870 align:middle line:84%
We've talked about
relationships.

00:25:07.870 --> 00:25:08.980 align:middle line:90%


00:25:08.980 --> 00:25:11.260 align:middle line:84%
But let's talk a little
bit more about health.

00:25:11.260 --> 00:25:13.000 align:middle line:90%


00:25:13.000 --> 00:25:16.430 align:middle line:84%
And aging is a perfect
way to talk about this.

00:25:16.430 --> 00:25:18.240 align:middle line:84%
There's a lot of
complications that

00:25:18.240 --> 00:25:20.900 align:middle line:84%
come with the body
breaking down.

00:25:20.900 --> 00:25:23.790 align:middle line:84%
So you really don't believe that
the body needs to break down?

00:25:23.790 --> 00:25:24.349 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: No.

00:25:24.349 --> 00:25:25.640 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What do you do instead?

00:25:25.640 --> 00:25:28.390 align:middle line:90%


00:25:28.390 --> 00:25:29.860 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: You arrest time.

00:25:29.860 --> 00:25:34.950 align:middle line:84%
If you arrest time, stop
time, then everything

00:25:34.950 --> 00:25:41.420 align:middle line:84%
happens, whether it's
changing your money situation

00:25:41.420 --> 00:25:44.730 align:middle line:84%
or your relationship
or your health.

00:25:44.730 --> 00:25:50.100 align:middle line:84%
Everything will change if
you just stay in the now.

00:25:50.100 --> 00:25:53.890 align:middle line:84%
And the now is the
absence of the mind,

00:25:53.890 --> 00:25:56.150 align:middle line:90%
because the mind is time.

00:25:56.150 --> 00:25:58.770 align:middle line:84%
So if that you do, it
is just a make believe.

00:25:58.770 --> 00:26:00.220 align:middle line:90%
The mind is a make believe.

00:26:00.220 --> 00:26:02.340 align:middle line:90%
And we all do that.

00:26:02.340 --> 00:26:03.942 align:middle line:84%
When we go to
sleep, what happens?

00:26:03.942 --> 00:26:04.775 align:middle line:90%
The mind disappears.

00:26:04.775 --> 00:26:05.920 align:middle line:90%


00:26:05.920 --> 00:26:08.240 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Well, the mind,
though, we create so much

00:26:08.240 --> 00:26:09.865 align:middle line:90%
with the mind that seems real.

00:26:09.865 --> 00:26:11.740 align:middle line:84%
So you're saying we're
just making it all up?

00:26:11.740 --> 00:26:15.360 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: See, the mind creates
only a very limited reality.

00:26:15.360 --> 00:26:17.440 align:middle line:84%
It cannot create an
unlimited reality.

00:26:17.440 --> 00:26:21.150 align:middle line:90%


00:26:21.150 --> 00:26:26.250 align:middle line:84%
Maybe the mind conceives
of, let's say, $1 billion.

00:26:26.250 --> 00:26:27.900 align:middle line:90%
That also a limited reality.

00:26:27.900 --> 00:26:29.770 align:middle line:84%
But it cannot do
anything to the body.

00:26:29.770 --> 00:26:33.070 align:middle line:90%


00:26:33.070 --> 00:26:35.210 align:middle line:90%
Now you will be a billionaire.

00:26:35.210 --> 00:26:37.050 align:middle line:84%
I know so many
billionaires with cancer.

00:26:37.050 --> 00:26:38.105 align:middle line:90%
And then they are crying.

00:26:38.105 --> 00:26:38.909 align:middle line:90%


00:26:38.909 --> 00:26:40.450 align:middle line:84%
So they cannot do
anything with that.

00:26:40.450 --> 00:26:41.660 align:middle line:90%


00:26:41.660 --> 00:26:46.180 align:middle line:84%
I think a person who is
very healthy with no money,

00:26:46.180 --> 00:26:51.975 align:middle line:84%
his life is better off than
having cancer and money.

00:26:51.975 --> 00:26:54.710 align:middle line:90%


00:26:54.710 --> 00:26:59.100 align:middle line:84%
So I'm not saying be poor,
but you can have both.

00:26:59.100 --> 00:27:00.850 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: How do you
suggest, though,

00:27:00.850 --> 00:27:03.874 align:middle line:84%
having both money and
happiness and health?

00:27:03.874 --> 00:27:05.290 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: Yeah,
that is the ideal.

00:27:05.290 --> 00:27:06.730 align:middle line:90%


00:27:06.730 --> 00:27:07.750 align:middle line:90%
That is the ideal.

00:27:07.750 --> 00:27:09.460 align:middle line:90%
Why do you polarize?

00:27:09.460 --> 00:27:12.610 align:middle line:84%
That's why I say
that God is not poor.

00:27:12.610 --> 00:27:13.980 align:middle line:90%


00:27:13.980 --> 00:27:15.730 align:middle line:84%
That is what all
of the religions

00:27:15.730 --> 00:27:20.130 align:middle line:84%
are teaching, that God
and money are separate.

00:27:20.130 --> 00:27:21.760 align:middle line:90%


00:27:21.760 --> 00:27:24.680 align:middle line:84%
That's why I tell people
that God loves money

00:27:24.680 --> 00:27:26.011 align:middle line:90%
more than you do.

00:27:26.011 --> 00:27:28.720 align:middle line:90%


00:27:28.720 --> 00:27:30.590 align:middle line:90%
He loves fun.

00:27:30.590 --> 00:27:31.551 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Fun?

00:27:31.551 --> 00:27:32.550 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: God loves fun.

00:27:32.550 --> 00:27:33.300 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Happiness.

00:27:33.300 --> 00:27:34.961 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: He's a party animal.

00:27:34.961 --> 00:27:37.471 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:27:37.471 --> 00:27:38.720 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: God is a party animal.

00:27:38.720 --> 00:27:39.969 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: He's a party animal.

00:27:39.969 --> 00:27:42.300 align:middle line:84%
Then you have a very
bad concept of God.

00:27:42.300 --> 00:27:43.710 align:middle line:90%


00:27:43.710 --> 00:27:47.610 align:middle line:84%
In the Hindu tradition,
it's very different.

00:27:47.610 --> 00:27:52.177 align:middle line:84%
There is Krishna, who is a
dancer and who is a musician.

00:27:52.177 --> 00:27:53.510 align:middle line:90%
And he has a lot of girlfriends.

00:27:53.510 --> 00:27:54.810 align:middle line:90%
That bothers a lot of people.

00:27:54.810 --> 00:27:57.285 align:middle line:90%


00:27:57.285 --> 00:28:01.240 align:middle line:84%
And there is another god who is
a dancer, Shiva, Dancing Shiva.

00:28:01.240 --> 00:28:03.440 align:middle line:90%


00:28:03.440 --> 00:28:06.690 align:middle line:84%
So without dance and music,
the life will be miserable.

00:28:06.690 --> 00:28:08.130 align:middle line:90%


00:28:08.130 --> 00:28:12.370 align:middle line:84%
So we are talking about this
in Hollywood on a Friday.

00:28:12.370 --> 00:28:15.220 align:middle line:90%
This is a lot of fun here.

00:28:15.220 --> 00:28:17.690 align:middle line:90%


00:28:17.690 --> 00:28:21.330 align:middle line:84%
And if you just put
God on a pedestal

00:28:21.330 --> 00:28:28.920 align:middle line:84%
and then conceive of him, well,
God is here, and money is here.

00:28:28.920 --> 00:28:31.800 align:middle line:90%


00:28:31.800 --> 00:28:33.540 align:middle line:90%
God is not a killjoy.

00:28:33.540 --> 00:28:35.520 align:middle line:84%
We have created a
God who is a killjoy.

00:28:35.520 --> 00:28:37.350 align:middle line:90%


